{"tid":1624202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"姚連生打壓學生 藍絲老師接打人學生放學！","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T02:47:41.000Z","uid":2988,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"a626a7c160b973348294b216615280228ba45e63","tid":1624202,"uid":2988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:12:22.000Z","msg":"事源係有街坊係校門外地下<br />\n噴左恐嚇低form同學個名 - 何嘉源<br />\n結果學校即刻用黑膠遮住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vr4xvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvr4xvgg.jpg&h=d70e8b39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左表揚何嘉源同學 同埋防止膠袋線親人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁當然有同學去撕走佢啦<br />\n點知即刻有老師出黎<br />\n拉番撕膠袋既學生入學校 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZSK5Rd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZSK5Rd.jpg&h=63e0af3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F3Up5V6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF3Up5V6.png&h=bd21d5f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話要家長接放學先比佢地走<br />\n然後叫校門外既人唔好再搞事<br />\n仲話如果 何嘉源 同學有咩事<br />\n就會入個低form同學仔數<br />\n之後門口愈黎愈多人要求學校放人<br />\n過左2 3個鐘 <br />\n突然好多老師一齊渣車收工<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69CjaoY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69CjaoY.jpg&h=84563e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知發現何嘉源同石文強(另一位欺凌低form同學)係其中一個車<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KqWjUSe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKqWjUSe.jpg&h=4a2c3e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpzQ1xu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpzQ1xu.png&h=0e8508c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbqkEjb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbqkEjb.jpg&h=6b9ff62d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最尾搞左幾個鐘先完到件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450e33ff560d126f2b773e804258c65d17b1bfe8","tid":1624202,"uid":2988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TP5Qsi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TP5Qsi.jpg&h=e32f7d82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n接放學架車"},{"pid":"b19ee37c53efb7edd4ded939501f8ef166987cf0","tid":1624202,"uid":2988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"450e33ff560d126f2b773e804258c65d17b1bfe8","tid":1624202,"uid":2988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TP5Qsi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TP5Qsi.jpg&h=e32f7d82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n接放學架車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucudZkM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FucudZkM.jpg&h=163712fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a86477ba05997fed6e53edadd45f147e9a854e7","tid":1624202,"uid":2988,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DGxK504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDGxK504.jpg&h=bb16e649&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期二齊去接放學<br />\n要求學校交代點解要用低form學生做籌碼<br />\n要求學校交出何嘉源</span></span>"},{"pid":"c86804c0b2e480699a591d7ac2d1cf9ce860a1b1","tid":1624202,"uid":2988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:17:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04d9f6128844f0ca0618ad6454041d758d6da35e","tid":1624202,"uid":2988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:17:46.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"24f618b470831913ca98db97822061c0047ee6ef","tid":1624202,"uid":2988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:17:56.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid"